LanguageData.ArachnaeQueen_Race.label: Arachne Empress
LanguageData.ArachnaeQueen_Race.description: The Arachne Empress is the only individual in the Arachne nest group that can give birth to a master insect, and as the top of the pyramid of nest group consciousness, she has the great mission of guiding the Arachne colony.The nest group is operated with extremely high efficiency due to the group consciousness network formed by the Cylink between her and the insect tribes under her control.However, if the Empress dies, all of the colonies under her will perish.
